Value: Cirrus Networks Holdings Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides information technology (IT) services and related third-party products in Australia. The company also offers advisory services for strategic plans, architecture, governance, procurement, cloud, IOT, and program and asset management; integration services, such as connectivity and communication, data center, collaboration, security, and project management and people services; managed services; and infrastructure services. Cirrus Networks Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Perth, Australia.
